flowchart TD
    A[TS File Edit] --> B[tsc --noEmit]
    B --> C{Type Errors?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Block: TS-TYPE-001]
    C -- No --> E[eslint + @typescript-eslint]
    E --> F{Lint Errors?}
    F -- Yes --> D
    F -- No --> G[prettier --check]
    G --> H[vitest run]
    H --> I{Tests Pass?}
    I -- No --> D
    I -- Yes --> J[Merge]
